description: Redevelopment of the site to provide a residential mixed-use development of 6 buildings between 12 and 20 storeys, plus two basement levels, comprising 806 residential units, including affordable housing, together with ancillary uses including a concierge/management suite, a business suite and leisure facilities; flexible commercial uses at ground and first floor including retail, financial and professional services, restaurant/caf and bar uses, healthcare facilities, a crche and gallery space (A1/A2/A3/A4 and D1 uses); car and cycle parking at basement level; extension and landscaping of the riverwalk and provision of public open space.
